  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK838">
<l>maiya loruvaṉ kaḷittaṟṟāṟ pētaitaṉ</l>
<l>kaiyoṉ ṟuṭaimai peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fool happening to possess something is like the intoxication of one who is (already) giddy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
